job_details.Functieomschrijving:
* Designing, developing, and implementing end-to-end web applications using modern frameworks and technologies
     * Building efficient and scalable back-end systems and APIs for seamless data integration
     * Creating intuitive user interfaces and engaging user experiences using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

job_details.full_text:
Full Stack Developer

* Designing, developing, and implementing end-to-end web applications using modern frameworks and technologies
     * Building efficient and scalable back-end systems and APIs for seamless data integration
     * Creating intuitive user interfaces and engaging user experiences using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
     * Collaborating with interdisciplinary teams to gather requirements and translate them into technical solutions

profile_classification.rationale: The job description focuses on general full-stack development, including web applications, back-end systems, and APIs, without mentioning any specific generative AI technologies, LLMs, or related frameworks. The tasks described, such as designing, developing, testing, and providing technical support for web applications, fall under traditional software engineering and do not align with the core responsibilities of an ML Engineer or GenAI Engineer as defined in the coding book. The mention of 'staying up to date with the latest trends' is too general to indicate a focus on AI.
